   7:funsape/device/sevenSegmentsDisplay.cpp **** //! @details        This file provides driver interface with the seven segments
   8:funsape/device/sevenSegmentsDisplay.cpp **** //!                     display with support to both common anode and common
   9:funsape/device/sevenSegmentsDisplay.cpp **** //!                     cathode displays. The following special characters were
  10:funsape/device/sevenSegmentsDisplay.cpp **** //!                     also implemented: dash, H, i, j, L, n, O, P, q, r, S, t,
  11:funsape/device/sevenSegmentsDisplay.cpp **** //!                     U, y, display off.
